      "settings": {
        "heading": "<strong>Why Choose PostJoy T20 Electric Bike?</strong>",
        "heading_size": "title-md",
        "heading_alignment": "text-left md:items-end md:flex-row",
        "heading_tag": "h2",
        "subheading": "",
        "description": "<p>The <strong>PostJoy T20</strong> is where classic retro aesthetics meet modern urban performance. Inspired by timeless motorcycle design, the T20 is crafted for riders who want to make a statement while enjoying a smooth, powerful ride across city streets and coastal paths alike.</p><p>Powered by a formidable <strong>2500W peak motor</strong>, the T20 offers effortless acceleration and a <strong>30 MPH top speed</strong>, making daily commutes and weekend cruises faster and more exciting. Its high-capacity 48V 20Ah battery ensures you stay on the move, delivering an impressive <strong>55-mile PAS range</strong> that lets you explore without range anxiety.</p><p>Designed for ultimate stability, the <strong>20\"x4.0\" fat tires</strong> and <strong>full suspension system</strong> iron out bumps in the road, providing a \"floating on air\" feel whether you're on pavement or sand. With the cutting-edge <strong>NFC smart unlock</strong> for keyless convenience and a bold retro silhouette, the T20 isn't just a bike—it’s the ultimate fusion of <strong>vintage style and electric freedom</strong>.</p>",
        "button_label": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "button_external": false,
        "button_icon": true,
