            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/393a2c4dab2b6a867a84cfb03689bbc8.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p><strong>48V 20Ah</strong> Removable Battery<br/><br/></p>",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>48V 20Ah high-capacity battery</strong> delivers a massive <strong>55-mile PAS range</strong>, providing the ultimate balance of power and endurance. With its <strong>removable design</strong>, you can easily <strong>charge anywhere</strong> and enjoy the freedom to explore deeper into the wild. Reliable, convenient, and built for <strong>long-distance thrills</strong>.<br/><br/></p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
