          }
        },
        "item_6M3dHz": {
          "type": "item",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 96,
            "item_margin_bottom": 70,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2026-04-17_113813_102.png",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p><strong> Full Suspension System</strong><br/>Ride Smooth, Dominate the Wild</p>",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>PostJoy GT16</strong> is engineered with a professional-grade full suspension system, transforming the roughest trails into your personal playground. At the front, the <strong>high-travel hydraulic fork</strong> is built to soak up heavy hits and high-speed vibrations, while the <strong>rear monoshock</strong> provides exceptional stability, ensuring your rear wheel stays planted for maximum traction during hill attacks.</p><p>Whether you're sticking a landing from a backyard jump, shredding through muddy mountain tracks, or navigating bumpy urban shortcuts, the GT16’s suspension delivers a <strong>perfectly balanced, stable, and plush ride</strong>. Combined with its agile <strong>99 lbs lightweight frame</strong>, you get a machine that doesn't just ride—it conquers any terrain with total control and comfort.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
